texts.content: {"text":"1. Osmonlardagi va yerdagi narsalar \nAllohga tasbih aytdi. \nU zot Aziyz va Hakiymdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,85]}]}

{"text":"2. Osmonlaru yerning mulki Unikidir. \nU tiriltirur va o`ldirur va U har bir narsaga qodirdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,93]}]}

{"text":"3. U avval va oxir, oshkor va pinhondir. \nVa U har bir narsani biluvchidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,75]}]}

{"text":"4. U osmonlaru yerni olti kunda yaratib, \nso`ngra (Zoti va ulug`ligiga munosib suratda) Arshga yuksalgan Zotdir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,113]}]}

{"text":"Yerga nima kirganini ham, undan nima chiqqanini ham, osmondan nima tushganini ham, unga nima chiqqanini ham biladir. \nU, qayerda bo`lsangiz ham, siz bilan birga. \nAlloh qilayotgan amallaringizni ko`rib turuvchidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,214]}]}

{"text":"5. Osmonlaru yerning mulki Unikidir va barcha ishlar Allohning O`zigagina qaytadir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,83]}]}

{"text":"6. Kechasini kunduzga kiritadi, kunduzni kechasiga kiritadi va U ko`ksingizdagi narsani ham yaxshi biluvchidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,111]}]}

{"text":"7. Allohga va Uning Rasuliga iymon keltiringlar hamda sizlarni xalifa qilib qo`ygan narsalardan ehson qilinglar. Bas, sizlardan iymon keltirgan va ehson qilganlarga ulkan ajr bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,182]}]}

{"text":"8. Sizlarga nima bo`ldiki, Allohga iymon keltirmaysizlar? Holbuki, Payg`ambar sizlarni Robbilaringizga iymon keltirishga chaqirib turibdi. U zot sizlardan ahd olgan edi. \nAgar iymon keltiruvchi bo`lsalaringiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,209]}]}

{"text":"9. U zot sizlarni zulmatlardan nurga chiqarish uchun O`z bandasiga ravshan oyatlarni tushiradi. \nVa, albatta, Alloh sizlarga shafqatli va rahimlidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,149]}]}

{"text":"10. Sizlarga nima bo`ldiki, \nAllohning yo`lida ehson qilmaysizlar? \nHolbuki, osmonlaru yerning merosi Allohnikidir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,116]}]}

{"text":"Sizlardan hech kim fathdan ilgari ehson qilganlarga va urushda qatnashganlarga barobar bo`la olmas. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,100]}]}

{"text":"Ularning darajalari fathdan so`ng ehson qilganlardan va urushda qatnashganlardan \nko`ra ulug`dir. Alloh barchaga yaxshilikni va'da qilgan. Va Alloh nima qilayotganlaringizdan xabardordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,187]}]}

{"text":"11. Allohga yaxshi qarz beradigan kishi bormi?! Bas, U zot unga bir necha marta ko`paytirib qaytaradi va unga karamli ajr bor.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,126]}]}

{"text":"12. Mo`min va mo`minalarni ularning oldilarida \nva o`ng taraflarida nurlari harakat qilayotgan holda ko`rgan kuningda, Sizlarga bugungi kunning xushxabari, daraxtlari ostidan suvlari oqib turgan jannatlardir. U joyda abadiy qolajaksiz. Bu esa, aynan ulkan yutuqdir (deyilur).","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,275]}]}

{"text":"13. Munofiq va munofiqalar iymonlilarga: \nTo`xtab turinglar, biz ham nuringizdan bir oz olaylik, degan va ularga: Ortingizga qayting hamda \nnur qidiring, deyilgan kunda.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,173]}]}

{"text":" Bas, ularning orasiga eshigi bor qo`rg`on urilur. Uning ichida rahmat, tashqarisida  oldida azobdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,102]}]}

{"text":"14. Ularga (munofiqlar): \nBiz siz bilan birga emasmidik?!  deb nido qilurlar. \nUlar: Xuddi shunday. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,104]}]}

{"text":"Lekin sizlar Allohning amri kelguncha o`zingizni o`zingiz fitnaga duchor qildingiz, ko`z tikib kutdingiz, shubha qildingiz va sizlarni xomxayollar g`ururga ketkazdi. Sizlarni Alloh haqida aldamchi aldab qo`ydi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,210]}]}

{"text":"15. Bugun sizlardan ham, \nkufr keltirganlardan ham to`lov olinmas. Joylaringiz jahannamda, u sizning egangizdir. Qanday ham yomon borar joy!  derlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,151]}]}

{"text":"16. Iymon keltirganlar uchun Allohning zikriga \nva nozil bo`lgan haqqa qalblari yumshash, \nayni chog`da, oldin kitob berilgan, so`ng muddat o`tishi bilan qalblari qotib qolgan, ko`plari fosiq bo`lganlarga o`xshamaslik vaqti kelmadimi?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,235]}]}

{"text":"17. Shuni bilinglarki, albatta Alloh o`lik yerni tiriltirur. Darhaqiqat, sizlarga oyatlarni bayon qildik, shoyadki, aql yuritsangizlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,135]}]}

{"text":"18. Albatta, sadaqa qiluvchi erkagu ayol hamda Allohga qarzi hasana beruvchilarga (savob) \nko`paytirib berilur. Ularga karamli ajr ham bor.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,139]}]}

{"text":"19. Allohga va Uning Payg`ambarlariga iymon keltirgan kishilar, ana o`shalar, siddiqlardir va Robbilari huzuridagi shohidlardir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,129]}]}

{"text":"Ularning ajrlari va nurlari bor. \nKufr keltirganlar va oyatlarimizni yolg`onga chiqargan kishilar, ana o`shalar do`zax egalaridir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,130]}]}

{"text":"20. Bilingki, albatta, bu dunyo hayoti o`yin, \nko`ngil ermagi va zeb-ziynatdan, o`zaro faxrlanishdan, mol-mulkni va bola-chaqani \nko`paytirishdan iboratdir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,157]}]}

{"text":"U, xuddi, o`simligi dehqonlarni ajablantirgan yomg`irga o`xshaydir. Keyinroq bu o`simliklar quriydi va sarg`ayganini ko`rasan. So`ngra u \nxas-cho`pga aylanib ketadir. Oxiratda esa, qattiq azob bor, Allohdan mag`firat va rozilik bor. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,233]}]}

{"text":"Bu dunyo hayoti g`ururga ketkazuvchi matodan o`zga hech narsa emas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,67]}]}

{"text":"21. Robbingizning mag`firatiga va Allohga hamda \nUning Payg`ambarlariga iymon keltirganlar uchun tayyorlangan, kengligi osmonu yerning kengligicha \nbo`lgan jannatga musobaqalashing. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,182]}]}

{"text":"Ana o`sha, Allohning fazli. Kimga xohlasa, beradi. \nAlloh ulug` fazl egasidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,78]}]}

{"text":"22. Biror musiybatni paydo qilmasimizdan oldin u Kitobda bitilgan bo`lur, aks holda, yer yuzida va o`z shaxslaringizda sizga biror musiybat yetmas. Albatta, bu ish Alloh uchun osondir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,184]}]}

{"text":"23. Toki, ketgan narsaga qayg`urib, \nkelgan narsadan xursand bo`lmasligingiz uchun. \nAlloh barcha dimog`dor va maqtanchoqlarni suymas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,134]}]}

{"text":"24. Ular baxildirlar va kishilarni ham \nbaxillikka buyururlar. Kim yuz o`girsa, bas, \nAlloh behojat va maqtalgan Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,120]}]}

{"text":"25. Darhaqiqat, Biz Payg`ambarlarimizni \nravshan(narsa)lar ila yubordik va ular ila kitob hamda odamlar adolatda turishlari uchun mezon tushirdik. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,147]}]}

{"text":"Va temirni tushirdik  unda katta kuch-quvvat va odamlar uchun manfaatlar bor. Alloh kim O`ziga va Payg`ambarlariga g`oyibona yordam berayotganini bilishi uchun. Albatta, Alloh kuchli va aziyzdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,196]}]}

{"text":"26. Darhaqiqat, Nuh va Ibrohimni Payg`ambar qilib yubordik hamda Payg`ambarlikni va kitobni ikkovlarining zurriyotiga xos qildik. Ular orasida hidoyat topganlar bor, lekin ularning ko`plari fosiqlardir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,202]}]}

{"text":"27. So`ngra ularning ortidan Payg`ambarlarimizni ketma-ket yubordik va Iyso ibn Maryamni ham ortlaridan yubordik hamda unga Injilni berdik. Unga ergashganlarning qalblariga mehribonlik va rahimdillikni soldik. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,210]}]}

{"text":"Rohiblikni o`zlari chiqarib oldilar, Biz buni ularga farz qilmagan edik, faqat o`zlari Allohning roziligini tilab qildilar, lekin haqiqiy rioyasini qila olmadilar. Bas, ulardan iymon keltirganlariga ajrlarini berdik, lekin ularning ko`pi fosiqlardir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,250]}]}

{"text":"28. Ey, iymon keltirganlar! Allohga taqvo qilinglar va Uning Payg`ambariga iymon keltiringlar. U zot O`z rahmatidan sizlarga ikki hissa beradir va sizlarning yurishingizga nur beradir hamda sizlarni mag`firat qiladir. Alloh kechiruvchi, rahimli Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,252]}]}

{"text":"29. Toki kitob ahllari Allohning fazlidan hech narsaga qodir emasliklarini, fazl Allohning qo`lida bo`lib, xohlagan kishisiga berishini bilsinlar. \nAlloh ulug` fazl egasidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,174]}]}
